entries.journal_entry_description: Dakar wants you to hamper the Blackscale slaving operations by killing ten of the Wookiees they have marked for capture. Collect ten Blackscale tags which are used to mark specific Wookiees targeted for capture in the Kkowir Forest.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: The Wookiees that the Blackscale clan has tagged are located in the Kkowir forests. Reports have them living on a small strip of land in the western part of the forest. Dakar said it was just a little west of a cave hidden behind a waterfall.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Destroy ten of the Blackscale tagged Wookiees in the Kkowir forests. Without these Wookiee the Blackscale clan will be unable to fill a special order they are working on and lose face with the other clans. Not every Wookiee in the area will have been tagged.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Bring the tags you have collect back to Dakar and report on your success.
